INSERT INTO provider_intents (
                provider, currency, available_amount, min_fee_bps, 
                max_fee_bps, commitment_window, is_active, expires_at
            ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
            ON CONFLICT (provider, currency) 
            DO UPDATE SET
                available_amount = $3,
                min_fee_bps = $4,
                max_fee_bps = $5,
                commitment_window = $6,
                is_active = $7,
                expires_at = $8,
                updated_at = NOW()
